<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯？<delay20 />啊……
是<tag a="110" b="4" />啊。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我正在考慮一些事情。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我<tag a="110" b="0" />
在考慮離開<delay8 />
<tag a="110" b="8" />，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="24" />我總覺得在這寬廣世界的某處，<delay20 />
好像有人正痴痴地等著我<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="001_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">不要走！</message>
	<message label="001_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">祝你一路順風</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你來得正好，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在有空跟我聊一下嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我一直在煩惱<tag a="110" b="0" />
到底要不要離開這座島嶼。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="8" />雖然是個好地方，<delay20 />
但現在<tag a="110" b="10" />需要的東西<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是刺激啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">你不能走！</message>
	<message label="002_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">嗯，我知道了</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
你可知道這美麗的海洋彼端<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />究竟有著什麼嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想著想著，<delay20 />
就不禁覺得希望一探究竟<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我啊，<delay20 />想要離開<tag a="110" b="8" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />親眼確認實際上的狀況！</message>
	<message label="003_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">不要走！</message>
	<message label="003_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">路上小心喔</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" /><tag a="110" b="0" />
我對你來說是不可或缺的嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然你那麼說的話，我也不會再迷惘了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我不搬出去了！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />從今以後，<delay20 />
我也會繼續在<tag a="110" b="8" />上<delay8 />
享受和你一起生活的時光喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 />被<tag a="110" b="4" />
這樣挽留的話，<delay20 />
我不就無法拋下你不管了嗎<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />搬家計畫就此Cancel！<10_4 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />，
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今後也請繼續關照囉，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="12" />既然<tag a="110" b="4" />
都說到這個分上了，<delay20 />
那我就再考慮一下吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我決定了！不搬家啦！<delay frames="40" />
<tag a="110" b="4" />，
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今後就重新請你多多關照啦！<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你的話語讓我下定了決心！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我果然還是<delay20 />希望離開這座島！<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在<tag a="110" b="8" /><delay20 />
和你度過的時光<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我絕對不會忘記的。<pageBreak /><tag a="110" b="4" />，
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />以後也要保重喔，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="12" />雖然我從來沒想到<delay20 />
自己會有離開這座島的一天<tag a="110" b="0" />
但天下沒有不散的筵席。<pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要說我現在不難過，那一定是騙人的。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是不用擔心，<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="8" />的景色<delay20 />
會長存於我心中的，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />謝謝你一直以來的照顧，<delay8 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />！<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不用難過，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要好好活著，我們一定能再會，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
